column2: SELECT     s.specobjid, s.ra, s.dec, s.z,    &&& + cast(x.objId as varchar(#)) + &&&+ cast(x.objId as varchar(#)) + &&& as objID, p.ra, p.dec,    dbo.fPhotoTypeN(p.type) as type,    p.modelMag_u, p.modelMagErr_u,    p.modelMag_g, p.modelMagErr_g,    p.modelMag_r, modelMagErr_r,     p.modelMag_i, modelMagErr_i,    p.modelMag_z, modelMagErr_z,    p.u, p.g, p.r, p.i, p.z FROM #upload u       JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id       JOIN PhotoTag p ON p.objID = x.objID       JOIN SpecObjAll s ON p.objID = s.bestObjID ORDER by x.up_id
